channel.title: Using moparscape v4 error
channel.description:
When i run my server, and i type in my public IP and port # using moparscape 4 client, it loads up fine.. when i try logging in, it starts to log in and then disconnects me. The moparscape client has this in its log down below
Error: T2 - 126,134,134 - 18,0,0 - 67,111,109,98,97,116,32,76,101,118,101,108,58,32,48,10,78,-97,
No idea what that means. Is there any other webclients I can use?
